text: Fjällbacka is a locality in Tanum Municipality in Västra Götaland County in Sweden. In 2010, 859 people lived there. It is wellknown as a summer tourist resort. ==Fjällbacka people== *Swedish actress Ingrid Bergman lived there when visiting Sweden. *Swedish crime writer Camilla Läckberg grew up there. It is also the place where many books written by her are set. == References == Category:Settlements in Vastra Gotaland County
title: Fjällbacka
